      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Behrnu/ neka tai Lauſatai Behr-\nnu irr/ ſakka tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Iſplatti tawas Telts Wee-\ntu/ un iſplett tawa Dſihwoſta\nGardines/ ne kauejees/ pagar-\nrina tawas Wirwes/ un ſtipri-\nna tawas Wadsitchuſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tu iſlehſti pa labbo un\npa kreifo Rohku/ un taws Dſim-\nmuns eemantohs tohs Paga-\nnus/ un dſihwohs eekſch teem\npoſtiteim Piſſahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne bihſtees/ jo tu ne tap-\nft Rauna/ un ne kaunees/ jo tu\nne tapſi apkaunota/ jo tu aiſmir-\nfifi to Raunu tawas Imprawi-\nbas/ un to Neewafchanu tawas\nAtraitnibas tu wairs ne pee-\nminnefi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo taws * Darritajs irr\ntaws Wihrs/ KUNGS Zebaot\nirr winna Wahrs/ un tas\nSwehtajs eekſch Iſraeta irr taws\nPestitajs/ wiſch taps nofaukts\ntas Deews wiſſas Paſaules.\n* Eebr: Wall: Tawi Darritaji irr tawi\nWihti Zaur ſcho jafapioht tahs trihs Ihpa-\nſchibas eekſch tahs fwchtas Triadibs, kas\nweenâ Buſſchana irr, un ſche nofauktas tohp\ntas KUNG S Zebaot.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS irr tew\naſzinajs ka weenu atſtahtu/ un\nno Sirđs noſkunnufchu See-\nwu/ un ka weenu jaunu See-\nwu/ jepſchu tu nizzinata effi/\nfakka taws Deews.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Masu Azzuntrekli efmu es\ntewi acſtabjis / bet ar leelahm\nApschehloſchanahm gribbu este-\nwi ſaputzihaft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar masahm Duſmahm ef-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas buhſ man ka ta\nUhdenſ Noiis/ kur es ſwehreju,\ntam Noiis Uhdenim ne bij wair\npahr to Semini eet/ tapatt ef\nmu es ſwehrejs/ ka es wairs n\ngribbu pahr tewi duſmoht/ ned-\ntewi lammaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Kalni wirſifees/ u\nPakalni ſchaubifees/ bet manna\nSchehlaſtiba no tewim ne wirſ\nfees/ un ta Derriba manna Mee\nra ne ſchaubifees / fatka ta\nKUNGS taws Apſchehlotajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu Apbehdinata / zau\nWehtrahtm ſchaubita/ tu Ne-e\npreezinata/ raugi/ es liſchu ta\nwus Akminius Skaistuma / u\ndibbinaſchu tew us Sawireen\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tawis Lohaus darri\nſchu es no Kristalla / un tawa\nWahrtis no Rubina - Akmi-\nneem/ un wiſſu tawu Rohbeſch\nno iſwehleteem Akmineem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſi tawi Behru\nbuhſ no ta KUNGA mahzit\nun tas Meers tawu Behru\nbuhſ leels.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu tapſi zaur Taifutb\nſtiprinata. Tu buhſi tahfu\nBehdahm/ jo tu ne bihſees / u\nno Iſtruhzinaſchanas/ jo ta p-\ntewis ne atuahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/tee pulzeht ſapu\nzetees/(bet) ne zaur manni/ k\npre\n"
    }
  ],
